title: (Weds Full) Name the Fictional TV Town Game + Lunchbox Review’s Amy’s Sister New HGTV Show + We Reveal Why We Say ‘Morning Studio’
itunes:title: (Weds Full) Name the Fictional TV Town Game + Lunchbox Review’s Amy’s Sister New HGTV Show + We Reveal Why We Say ‘Morning Studio’
description:
We play a game where Bobby gives everyone the name of the fictional town…they just have to name the TV show.  Lunchbox reviews “Building Roots” on HGTV which stars Amy’s sister who he is jealous of.  We reveal the origin of our “morning studio” catch phrase.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
